# ЁЯза PART-4: RLS vs OLS тАФ Exam Friendly Table

| Need                                           | Use         |
| ---------------------------------------------- | ----------- |
| Only some **rows** visible                     | RLS         |
| Hide **measure / column / table**              | **OLS**     |
| Same table, different users see different rows | Dynamic RLS |
| Sensitive cost / salary measure                | **OLS**     |

